OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fwindy, with further showers through
OL,7,Fthe evening and overnight. Again, some
OL,8,Fof these will be on the heavy side,
OL,9,Fwith the risk of hail. Feeling chilly
OL,10,Fin brisk winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAnother day of sunny spells
OL,13,Fand showers is expected. Showers may
OL,14,Falso merge into some longer spells of
OL,15,Fheavy rain. Winds remaining brisk,
OL,16,Fthough gradually easing later in the
OL,17,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
