OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FSunshine and showers through Monday.
OL,7,FDrier and brighter to start on
OL,8,FTuesday, ahead of rain arriving from
OL,9,Fthe west. Wetter and windier again on
OL,10,FWednesday. Temperatures trending up a
OL,11,Flittle.
